<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="17">Hebeloma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
subsect. 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="17">
<taxonomicName genus="Crustuliniformia" lsidName="Crustuliniformia" pageId="0" pageNumber="17" rank="genus">Crustuliniformia</taxonomicName>
Quadr.
</emphasis>
; Doc. mycol. 14: 30, 1985 (
<normalizedToken originalValue="“1984”">&quot;1984&quot;</normalizedToken>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="17">
Cheilocystidia distinctly broadened at apex, base 
<normalizedToken originalValue="±">+/-</normalizedToken>
cylindrical, wall not thickened. Lamellae edge often with exuded drops.
</paragraph>
